<img src="/images/newicons/book.gif" width="15" height="15" alt="" style="vertical-align: text-top" />
<b>
Broken from the wars...
</b>
 <img alt="new" src="/images/new.gif" />
 <font class="small">[<a href="http://www.ralloszek.net/ubbthreads/showthreaded.php?Cat=&amp;Board=rp&amp;Number=14024&amp;page=0&amp;view=collapsed&amp;sb=5&amp;o=&amp;vc=1" target="_new">re: Descourge</a>]</font> 
